data.description: Popular great room floor plan with a split floor plan in the Award Winning Active Adult Community of Province!  Fabulous great room with gas fireplace, open to the kitchen with a huge island and beautiful staggered oak cabinetry.  The oversized backyard has a spacious patio and offers wonderful privacy with mature landscaping.  From the practical and spacious floor plan to the multitude of amenities here in Province, you'll love everything about this magnificent home.  Additional features in this home include:  bay window at the kitchen nook, soft water and RO system, front security door, gas pre-plump at backyard perfect for a BBQ or fire pit, built in cabinets at the laundry room, ceiling fans and window coverings throughout with sun shades off the back patio.  Welcome Home!
